headline: Average 401(k) balance in your 60s: How do you stack up?
summary: The average 401(k) balance for people in their 60s has hit a record high — but the median is far lower.

headline: Wells Fargo Downgrades Prudential Financial to Underweight, Lowers Price Target to $103
summary: Wells Fargo  analyst Wesley Carmichael   downgrades Prudential Financial (NYSE:PRU) from Equal-Weight to Underweight and lowers the price target from $115 to $103.
